::Feline::

She knew that once she had the third chip installed, then she would 
use that bot to create the distraction she needed to get her and 
HotRod out of there.  She wanted to try to take Skulletron with her, 
but then again, it seamed that the "every bot for it'self" was 
becoming a growing trend, except for a few soft sparked maximals.  
She smiled knowing that she would be able to take the famous bot 
RODIMUS PRIME, AKA HotRod with her.
